# Intermediate checkpoint files written by one-off fixup scripts in
# packages/db/scripts. Canonical records live in the database (AuditLog
# rows) — these JSONs are recovery state if a long script is interrupted
# mid-run, not committed artefacts.
docs/hero-fill-progress.json
docs/tricolon-fixup-progress.json

